config.splatcraft.splatfest_band_must_be:
Whether or not Splatfest Bands
must be held in any hand to
affect the player's ink type.
config.splatcraft.inkwell_changes_ink_co:
Whether or not Inkwells change
the ink color of entities on top
of one.
config.splatcraft.hurt_ink_squids_in_wat:
Whether or not to hurt Ink
Squids or players in squid
form when in water.
config.splatcraft.hurt_ink_squids_on_ene: Hurt Ink Squids On Enemy Ink

Whether or not to hurt Ink
Squids or players in squid
form when on enemy ink.
config.splatcraft.instant_squid_form_cha:
Whether or not the client waits
for the server's confirmation
to change squid form.
config.splatcraft.prevent_bob_view_when_: Prevent View Bobbing When In Squid Form
config.splatcraft.stage_block_radius.too: The radius at which to render stage blocks.
config.splatcraft.color_lock.tooltip:
Whether or not ink colors are
replaced with just a friendly
or hostile color.
Useful for color-blind users.
config.sodium.ink_biome_blend_fix.toolti:
Disables smooth biome blending
from Sodium to fix odd ink
blending between blocks.
